Title: Custom-Sorter for Service Descriptions
Component: multisite
State: open
Date: 2014-12-10 14:36:33
Targetversion: future
Class: phantasm

Implement a sorter which can accomplish this:

TEMP Unit1
TEMP Unit2
TEMP Unit3
PSU Unit1
PSU Unit2
PSU Unit3
FAN Unit1
FAN Unit2
FAN Unit3

can be sorted like this

TEMP Unit1
PSU Unit1
FAN Unit1
TEMP Unit2
PSU Unit2
FAN Unit2
TEMP Unit3
PSU Unit3
FAN Unit3

Howto:
Split service description at keyword, exchange elements, resort table

Feature is configurable via display options.
Maybe highlight service blocks of the same unit.
